parameters: \nc<Security Guard 1>Saki-chan again today... Lucky me. I'm glad I came to work.

\nc<Security Guard 2>How have you been? To come back after being attacked by a
thief... You must have really taken a liking to this place,
huh?

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>I'm just here because the company told me to come. If
there's nothing else, may I start working?
\nc<Security Guard 1>Hyaah, you're cold today. Well, that's fine too.
